<p>Hi<%= @user.display_name ? " #{@user.display_name}" : "" %>,</p>

<p>Your sign-in code is:</p>

<p style="font-size: 32px; font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.15em; padding: 16px 0;"><%= @short_code %></p>

<p>Enter this code in the browser where you requested it. It expires in 15 minutes.</p>

<p>Or sign in from any browser using this link:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Sign in", @url %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
